un second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When William Chauntrell Esquire was born in 1400, in Lancashire, England, his father, John Chauntrell, was 31 and his mother, Margery Cantrell, was 30. He had at least 1 daughter with Alice Cantrell of Kent. He died in 1439, in his hometown, at the age of 39."},"et":{"1400–1439":"1400–1439","1415–1455":"1415–1455","1400–1481":"1400–1481","–Female":"Surnud","1424–1520":"1424–1520","1426–1473":"1426–1473","1370–Male":"1370–Surnud","1370–1433":"1370–1433","<1424>":"1424","1426":"1426","1415":"1415","1424":"1424","1400":"1400","1433":"1433","1455":"1455","1520":"1520","1473":"1473","1481":"1481","1370":"1370","1439":"1439","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, England","<Of Barton, Eccles, Lancashire, England>":"Barton, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1400–1439":"1400–1439","1415–1455":"1415–1455","1400–1481":"1400–1481","–Female":"Kuollut","1424–1520":"1424–1520","1426–1473":"1426–1473","1370–Male":"1370–Kuollut","1370–1433":"1370–1433","<1424>":"1424","1426":"1426","1415":"1415","1424":"1424","1400":"1400","1433":"1433","1455":"1455","1520":"1520","1473":"1473","1481":"1481","1370":"1370","1439":"1439","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, England","<Of Barton, Eccles, Lancashire, England>":"Barton, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1400–1439":"1400–1439","1415–1455":"1415–1455","1400–1481":"1400–1481","–Female":"Décédée","1424–1520":"1424–1520","1426–1473":"1426–1473","1370–Male":"1370–Décédé","1370–1433":"1370–1433","<1424>":"1424","1426":"1426","1415":"1415","1424":"1424","1400":"1400","1433":"1433","1455":"1455","1520":"1520","1473":"1473","1481":"1481","1370":"1370","1439":"1439","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, Angleterre","<Of Barton, Eccles, Lancashire, England>":"Barton, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque William Chauntrell Esquire est né en 1400, à Lancashire, Angleterre, son père, 